      Business
    </h2>
    <h3
      class="max-w-2xl px-5 mt-2 text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-center text-gray-900 sm:mt-0 sm:px-0 sm:text-6xl"
    >
      Business logic
    </h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col w-full mt-0 lg:flex-row sm:mt-10 lg:mt-20">
      <div class="w-full max-w-md p-4 mx-auto mb-0 sm:mb-16 lg:mb-0 lg:w-1/3">
        <div
          class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-full p-20 mr-5 rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
        >

          <img src="../imgs/icons8-1-en-círculo-96.png" alt="" />
          <h4 class="relative mt-6 text-lg text-center font-bold">
            Consortium register
          </h4>
          <p class="relative mt-2 text-base text-center text-gray-600">
            The consortium registers and generates an account that will contain
            its own information and that of its members. To start operating, an
            initial payment will be required depending on the size of the
            consortium.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full max-w-md p-4 mx-auto mb-0 sm:mb-16 lg:mb-0 lg:w-1/3">
        <div
          class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-full p-20 mr-5 rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
        >

          <img src="../imgs/icons8-2-en-círculo-96.png" alt="" />
          <h4 class="relative mt-6 text-lg font-bold">Generate voting</h4>
          <p class="relative mt-2 text-base text-center text-gray-600">
            A vote is generated with the details of the proposal, accompanied by
            different voting options. Each vote may require, depending on the
            proposal, a minimum of participating members to be considered valid.
            Each vote will have a start date and an end date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full max-w-md p-4 mx-auto mb-16 lg:mb-0 lg:w-1/3">
        <div
          class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-full p-20 mr-5 rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
        >

          <img src="../imgs/icons8-3-en-círculo-96.png" alt="" />
          <h4 class="relative mt-6 text-lg font-bold text-center">
            Voting
          </h4>
          <p class="relative mt-2 text-base text-center text-gray-600">
            Each member may direct its stack of votes in the manner it deems
            necessary, so it is not mandatory to vote for only one option, but
            may divide his vote strategically in the proposed offers, if he/she
            so wishes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
